						<div class="postbody">I don't use macros. I don't ever have the use for them and also trying to use those would add another layer of complexity my code which is not needed. To keep code shorter and out of my way when I don't need it I put it in another file just for that main routine. No macros, but the code isn't hard to figure out. Besides, I never have that much code that is the same anyway.</div>

